    "ailments_description": "The most common ailments you can heal with Angelica sinensis are fatigue, which is alleviated due to its high iron content and its ability to increase red blood cell count, and asthma, as it has been shown to relax bronchial muscles and reduce inflammation. Additionally, its anti-diarrheal properties can help alleviate diarrhea by regulating bowel movements and reducing fluid loss. Hypertension is also effectively managed with Angelica sinensis, as it has been proven to lower blood pressure by reducing vascular resistance and enhancing vasodilation. Furthermore, rheumatoid arthritis symptoms are reduced with the plant's anti-inflammatory and immunomodulatory properties, which can inhibit the production of pro-inflammatory cytokines. Its properties also benefit anemia, menstrual disorders, inflammation, menstrual cramps, digestive issues, cough, eczema, migraines, anxiety, rheumatism, gastroenteritis, fever, menorrhagia, diabetes.",
